{"tid":901942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又Loop!】國泰今年將招聘1,800名新員工！現時IT部只有12名員工 無進一步裁員計劃","createTime":"2018-11-14T12:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T03:23:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1355acb658930ee95f792259a5d5994efd39d2be","tid":901942,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"立法會今日（14日）召開聯席會議，討論國泰航空發生940萬乘客資料外洩事件七個月後，始對外通報。外界指今次事件的肇因之一，是國泰於去年重組架構時，資訊科技部被大幅裁員有關，令黑客有機可乘。國泰顧客及商務總裁盧家培強調，裁員與事故無關聯，而目前該公司的資訊科技部有12名員工，今次事件後會繼續擴張團隊。國泰行政總裁何杲在會上表示，國泰無進一步裁員計劃。另外，國泰今年將招聘1,800名新員工，涵蓋前線及後援部門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/258795/國泰洩私隱-國泰-會繼續擴張it部-無裁員計劃-擬增聘1800人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F258795%2F%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E6%B4%A9%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0-%E6%9C%83%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5it%E9%83%A8-%E7%84%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E6%93%AC%E5%A2%9E%E8%81%981800%E4%BA%BA&d=pjepta7IDo9He3ZZvGfzZ49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=896bb5a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/258795/國泰洩私隱-國泰-會繼續擴張it部-無裁員計劃-擬增聘1800人</a>"},{"pid":"b395b5335c2105df670e6c587082a4f317556cf3","tid":901942,"uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"明年又loop過<br />\n<br />\nLoop到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fbb5523536bdbf8ba6d94d407627b78fd780d9","tid":901942,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b395b5335c2105df670e6c587082a4f317556cf3","tid":901942,"uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"明年又loop過<br />\n<br />\nLoop到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" clas